{"tid":97422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聊天頻道打「台灣國」 玩家被中國遊戲鎖帳號20年","createTime":"2017-01-27T15:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T05:22:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1364ceafb1208145141dd7af9415310c6b7f3eda","tid":97422,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:39:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>中國遊戲聊天打「台灣國」　玩家遭鎖20年</strong><br />\n2017年01月27日17:42<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170127/640_a162795f977fec9e023b1be371ec3d8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170127%2F640_a162795f977fec9e023b1be371ec3d8b.jpg&h=67017094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自巴哈姆特<br />\n<br />\n網友玩多人即時電競手機遊戲時，在聊天室打了一句「國服？台灣國服嗎？」，不僅被系統遮蔽成「國服？***服嗎？」帳號還被鎖了20年，讓他批：「果然是大中華的工商大作，每個大作都有除髒話外的禁言呢」。<br />\n<br />\n網友在《巴哈姆特》遊戲版發文指出，台灣英旗互動娛樂代理的手機遊戲《獵神》在台公測(中國遊戲名為《全民超神》，<span style=\"color: red;\">製作廠商為騰訊</span>)，就抓來玩玩看，上線後通過新手教學，接著在遊戲大廳看到有個人用簡體字發表「有人有玩國服嗎」，他打字回「國服？台灣國服嗎？」沒想到顯示出來變成「國服？***服嗎？」讓他玻璃心碎，質疑為什麼不能說台灣國？<br />\n<br />\n而且他發言的帳號還被鎖20年，要2038年才能解鎖，讓他批這款遊戲上市到台灣，也套用無言論自由，鎖帳號，果然是大中華的工商大作，每個大作都有除髒話外的禁言呢。<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然台灣代理商有留言回應這位網友，是啟用了自動封禁機制來維護遊戲環境</span>，不過該網友也回批：「不要用遊戲來干涉他人思想，貴公司上市的地方是台灣。言論自由」<br />\n<br />\n其他網友看到鎖帳號一事，也紛紛留言「笑死，看到這篇文，我也想刪遊戲了」、「佛心遊戲，代理商連無言論自由都完整代理了」、「你在台港澳上線而不是中國大陸阿，懂嗎?」、「刪game囉～連玩個遊戲都能這樣搞玩家，相信應該也撐不了多久」。<br />\n<br />\n（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170127/1045099/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flife%2F20170127%2F1045099%2F&d=WR3KeWjj0JuqOJLXqtgwAHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d24b3a78\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170127/1045099/</a>"},{"pid":"39bcd054a13948f1768e0a51a3fb9ac2a15b5cfa","tid":97422,"uid":78009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:41:30.000Z","msg":"十三億人玩就夠架喇，支那嘢就係圍威喂"},{"pid":"70ecce8748bd4004a27a300d754c50472c95395c","tid":97422,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"依家好多game繁體化得好成功，唔講真係唔知係大陸整 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa757702760ad3be30f52597837cfd54675f40bd","tid":97422,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家好多game繁體化得好成功，唔講真係唔知係大陸整 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇個樣都知大陸換湯唔換藥垃圾game"},{"pid":"ab360b010f52ca934a08ec0750a3bcb1f4e472f4","tid":97422,"uid":79519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de521a0cda290a43f5e97e30534aa19b5e5f50b","tid":97422,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"「你那裡讀書的？」<br />\n<br />\n「台灣國立藝術學院」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被BAM 廿年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb3e0c4dd308eff8cdf9ddbcc09863f4ff35ff3","tid":97422,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「你那裡讀書的？」<br />\n<br />\n「台灣國立藝術學院」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被BAM 廿年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db50bcd6b427e09bc419e6a121d27e6750b364c","tid":97422,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:33:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾game，不了"},{"pid":"7eb9e858d2abb1510a31ab3da28f4d715458501e","tid":97422,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,